00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:21,000
 The reason I believe that is because Romans chapter 3 actually says that.

379
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:26,000
 And so we have to start with the reality that you will need way more than religion

380
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,000
 to be saved.

