00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:47,000
 All of the emphasis would be on the guy doing the work.

413
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:51,000
 And the point is that's impossible.

414
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:56,000
 Just like it's impossible for a man to climb back up into his mother's womb

415
00:22:56,000 --> 00:23:00,000
 and be born again, it is impossible.

416
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:08,000
 It is impossible for you to be saved without being born from above,

417
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:11,000
 without a spiritual birth.

