00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:37,000
 See, water in the Old Testament was symbolic for cleansing,

427
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:42,000
 and Spirit was symbolic of new life.

428
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:46,000
 And so what Jesus is saying is, he's like, "Unless you're cleansed by God

429
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:53,000
 and unless you're given new life by God, you can't enter the kingdom of God."

