00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:57,000
 So then in verse 6, he says, "That which is born of the flesh is flesh.

431
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,000
 That which is born of the Spirit is spirit."

432
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:03,000
 So his point is, look, you have to have two births.

433
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:07,000
 You need to be born of the flesh as a human being,

434
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:09,000
 but then you have to be born of the Spirit.

435
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:13,000
 The Spirit of God actually has to do a miraculous work in you.

