00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:16,000
 in which he imparts new spiritual life to us."

452
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:19,000
 Bruce Demarest puts it this way,

453
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:25,000
 "Regeneration is that work of the Spirit at conversion

454
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:29,000
 that renews the heart and life, the inner self,

455
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:35,000
 thus restoring the person's intellectual, volitional, moral, emotional,

456
00:25:35,000 --> 00:25:38,000
 and relational capacities to do what?

457
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:43,000
 To know, love, and serve God."

458
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,000
 So do you understand what's happening here?

