00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:28,000
 But as you're hearing the gospel and responding to the gospel,

469
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:31,000
 which is what you should do,

470
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:35,000
 a miracle is taking place in your heart.

471
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:40,000
 The Spirit of God is awakening your mind and your heart

472
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:45,000
 to embrace the truth and to receive Jesus.

473
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,000
 This is the idea of regeneration.

474
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:49,000
 So if you're a Christian, you just need to know

475
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:55,000
 you are actually a walking miracle, and God gets the credit for you.

